Not a good repack, this one is.  The videos have been re-encoded to a lower resolution and quality, which is fair enough since they're just disposable loading screen garbage, but most annoyingly the in-game voices have been compressed very badly, so that everyone sounds like they're talking from a CB radio.  If that sort of shit bothers you like it does me, then look elsewhere.

To all the guys who have globe converter dissapperaing:
#1:Start globe converter. It dissappears or doesn't show up.
#2:Leave your PC undisturbed for 1-2 hours. When I mean undisturbed i mean no gaming and no resource consuming activities.
#3:To see if the converting has been finished, start task manager and check if globe converter is still running. If it is not running, it means that converting is over. If it is running you gotta wait.
